Program: Outlook
Title: Montserrat Volcano
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03kbrjl
Last Broadcast Date: Not available
Two-thirds of the population of Montserrat left after the 1997 volcano eruption. Now there is an open-door policy encouraging people to return. Also, a consideration of the North-South divide in Korea with South Koreans visiting the North and a Korean author with an unusual perspective. Finally, a look at the art of intuition, 'facts hidden in the brain'. Show less